00:18:00,879 --> 00:18:03,109
Do you like singing?

241
00:18:03,182 --> 00:18:06,413
Yes, I do, miss,
and no, I don't,
if you know what I mean.

242
00:18:06,485 --> 00:18:09,181
I'm sorry.
Either you do
or you don't.

