I signed a few checks.
Do that all the time.

288
00:21:23,749 --> 00:21:27,742
My sister's child.
We always take care
of our own. Like to do it.

289
00:21:27,819 --> 00:21:30,185
I like being here,
too, UncleJim.
You like bein' here.

290
00:21:30,255 --> 00:21:32,519
Uh-huh.
You met
your cousins?

291
00:21:32,591 --> 00:21:34,650
Yes.
You met your
Aunt Grace?

292
00:21:34,726 --> 00:21:37,320
Yes.
And you like
bein' here?

293
