Terry!
Sorry, ma'am.

648
00:42:34,652 --> 00:42:36,643
[Mumbles]

649
00:42:37,755 --> 00:42:39,746
[Engine Starting, Revving]

650
00:43:41,785 --> 00:43:45,721
All right.
I'll stay home.

651
00:43:46,724 --> 00:43:48,715
I'll say you will.

652
00:43:50,694 --> 00:43:54,653
Going to the ball
wasn't my idea.
You were pretty anxious.

653
00:43:54,732 --> 00:43:57,326
