to be getting any
foolish ideas about him.

657
00:44:07,378 --> 00:44:12,782
I'm not!
Oh, no?
What about that picture you
cut out of the newspaper?

658
00:44:12,850 --> 00:44:15,944
Who was that?
Ted Drake, that's who.

659
00:44:16,020 --> 00:44:20,252
I just cut it out.
There wasn't any reason
for cutting it out.

660
00:44:20,324 --> 00:44:23,657
I suppose there isn't any reason
for keeping it hidden
in that book, either.

661
00:44:23,727 --> 00:44:27,629
In what book?
In what book!
In that book!

662
00:44:27,698 --> 00:44:30,360
That?
Stop being a silly girl.

663
00:44:30,434 --> 00:44:34,097
Get that picture, tear it up
and throw it away this minute.

664
00:44:34,171 --> 00:44:37,231
That's exactly
what I'm going to do.

665
00:44:37,307 --> 00:44:39,502
See?
I'm tearing it up.

666
00:44:39,576 --> 00:44:41,840
