Talking?

671
00:44:57,461 --> 00:45:01,522
Oh! I must have been
talking to myself.

672
00:45:01,598 --> 00:45:05,932
I'm sorry to interrupt, miss,
but everything's been arranged
and you're going to the ball.

673
00:45:06,003 --> 00:45:09,097
