Indeed you are. UncleJason
is still in Washington.

674
00:45:09,173 --> 00:45:11,107
But Aunt Grace said...
They'll be there.

675
00:45:11,175 --> 00:45:13,234
They won't arrive
until midnight.

676
00:45:13,310 --> 00:45:15,676
They'll be there
long before that.

677
00:45:15,746 --> 00:45:17,907
No, they won't, miss.
Everything's been changed.

678
00:45:17,981 --> 00:45:20,575
You'll be there and back
before they even arrive.
How will I go?

679
00:45:20,651 --> 00:45:22,482
In your car.
And it's a pippin.

680
00:45:22,553 --> 00:45:25,044
Who'll take me?
You'll have an escort
of six white bikes.

681
00:45:25,122 --> 00:45:27,317
