Bikes, miss.
Motor police.

682
00:45:29,493 --> 00:45:32,053
And there they are.

683
00:45:33,664 --> 00:45:35,791
You mean l...
I'm to go with them?

684
00:45:35,866 --> 00:45:37,925
They'll get you there
before you can say
"Jack Robinson."

685
00:45:38,001 --> 00:45:39,901
Mike told them
you were in a hurry.
Mike?

686
00:45:39,970 --> 00:45:43,565
My brother, miss. These lads
work with him. They borrowed
the commissioner's car.

687
00:45:43,640 --> 00:45:46,837
Now remember, miss.
You're not to stay
a minute later than 12:00.

688
00:45:46,910 --> 00:45:50,573
