Have the time of your life!
Remember 12:00!

696
00:46:13,370 --> 00:46:17,170
[Sirens Wailing]

697
00:46:19,710 --> 00:46:22,201
[Horn Honking]

698
00:46:30,788 --> 00:46:33,279
