00:52:01,985 --> 00:52:03,953
Who's that
pretty little girl?
I don't know.

788
00:52:04,020 --> 00:52:06,921
Her face is familiar.
I can't figure out
where I met her.

789
00:52:14,931 --> 00:52:17,161
